{
  "info": {
    "name": "Trends API",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": "Trends FastAPI — indicator engine + futures (Support/Bullish) for live ticker data."
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:5001",
      "description": "Change to your deployed host, e.g. http://192.168.29.204:5001"
    },
    {
      "key": "ticker",
      "value": "nifty",
      "description": "Ticker symbol (case-insensitive, matched as uppercase internally)"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/health",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "health"]
            },
            "description": "Returns {\"status\": \"ok\"} when the app is running."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/health" }
              },
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\"status\": \"ok\"}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Seed",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Seed ticker from Excel",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/seed/{{ticker}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "seed", "{{ticker}}"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "file",
                  "type": "file",
                  "src": "",
                  "description": "Excel (.xlsx) file containing OHLCV history."
                },
                {
                  "key": "sheet",
                  "type": "text",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Optional: sheet name to read. If omitted, the first sheet is used.",
                  "disabled": true
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Upload an Excel (.xlsx) file to seed historical OHLCV data for a ticker.\n\nColumn detection (automatic):\n1. Header scan — looks for a row in the first 20 rows with Date, Close, Open, High, Low headers (case-insensitive). Data starts after that row.\n2. Fallback — if no header found, assumes fixed layout: B=Date, W=Close, X=Open, Y=High, Z=Low.\n\nRows with missing or non-numeric OHLCV values are silently skipped.\nResets all existing state for the ticker before loading.\nSwitches the ticker to live mode after loading so that subsequent PUTs are idempotent.\n\nOptional form field `sheet`: name of the sheet to read. If omitted, uses the first sheet.\n\nReturns:\n  ticker, sheet, bars_loaded, status, column_detection"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 — Seeded (header detected)",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/seed/{{ticker}}" },
                "body": {
                  "mode": "formdata",
                  "formdata": [{ "key": "file", "type": "file", "src": "" }]
                }
              },
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"ticker\": \"NIFTY\",\n  \"sheet\": \"Sheet1\",\n  \"bars_loaded\": 5383,\n  \"status\": \"seeded\",\n  \"column_detection\": \"header row detected\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "200 — Seeded (fallback columns)",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/seed/{{ticker}}" }
              },
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"ticker\": \"NIFTY\",\n  \"sheet\": \"Nifty-20.12.2024\",\n  \"bars_loaded\": 5383,\n  \"status\": \"seeded\",\n  \"column_detection\": \"fallback (B/W/X/Y/Z)\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "400 — Sheet not found",
              "status": "Bad Request",
              "code": 400,
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/seed/{{ticker}}" }
              },
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"detail\": \"Sheet 'WrongName' not found. Available sheets: ['Sheet1', 'Sheet2']\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "400 — Invalid file",
              "status": "Bad Request",
              "code": 400,
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/seed/{{ticker}}" }
              },
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"detail\": \"Could not parse file — make sure it is a valid .xlsx file\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Ticker",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List all tickers",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/tickers",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "tickers"]
            },
            "description": "Returns a list of all ticker symbols currently loaded in memory."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/tickers" }
              },
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"tickers\": [\"NIFTY\", \"BANKNIFTY\"]\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete ticker",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/tickers/{{ticker}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "tickers", "{{ticker}}"]
            },
            "description": "Remove a ticker from memory. All state and history is discarded. Any open SSE streams for this ticker receive no further events. Returns 404 if the ticker is not loaded."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 — Deleted",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "DELETE",
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/tickers/{{ticker}}" }
              },
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"ticker\": \"NIFTY\",\n  \"status\": \"deleted\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "404 — Not found",
              "status": "Not Found",
              "code": 404,
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "DELETE",
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/tickers/{{ticker}}" }
              },
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"detail\": \"Ticker 'NIFTY' not found\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Update ticker (current day)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/update/{{ticker}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "update", "{{ticker}}"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "force",
                  "value": "false",
                  "description": "Set to true to force futures recompute on every tick (default: false = compute once per day)",
                  "disabled": true
                }
              ]
            },
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"date\":  \"23-Dec-2024\",\n  \"close\": 23963.0,\n  \"open\":  24099.0,\n  \"high\":  24099.0,\n  \"low\":   23963.0\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Post a live OHLCV bar for the ticker. Recomputes all indicators and returns a TickerSnapshot.\n\nFutures (support / bullish) are computed ONCE per day on the first tick, using:\n  - support  : prev day's high as d+1 anchor; find trial where BP[d+3]=BP[d+2]\n  - bullish  : find trial where BP[d+4]=BP[d+3] with all four future bars = trial\n\nAdd ?force=true to recompute futures on every tick (useful for testing).\n\nWhen the date changes, the previous live bar is promoted to a checkpoint and a `warning` field appears in the response."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 — Full snapshot (after 100+ bars seeded)",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "PUT",
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/update/{{ticker}}" },
                "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"date\":  \"23-Dec-2024\",\n  \"close\": 23963.0,\n  \"open\":  24099.0,\n  \"high\":  24099.0,\n  \"low\":   23963.0\n}"
                }
              },
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"ticker\": \"NIFTY\",\n  \"date\": \"23-Dec-2024\",\n  \"close\": 23963.0,\n  \"open\": 24099.0,\n  \"high\": 24099.0,\n  \"low\": 23963.0,\n  \"hl\": 24199.0,\n  \"avg\": 23850.42,\n  \"ema5\": 23981.27,\n  \"ema20\": 23744.58,\n  \"rsi\": 48.32,\n  \"support\": 24215.80,\n  \"bullish\": 23958.47,\n  \"warning\": null\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "200 — Date changed (day rollover)",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "PUT",
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/update/{{ticker}}" },
                "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"date\":  \"24-Dec-2024\",\n  \"close\": 24100.0,\n  \"open\":  23963.0,\n  \"high\":  24120.0,\n  \"low\":   23900.0\n}"
                }
              },
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"ticker\": \"NIFTY\",\n  \"date\": \"24-Dec-2024\",\n  \"close\": 24100.0,\n  \"open\": 23963.0,\n  \"high\": 24120.0,\n  \"low\": 23900.0,\n  \"hl\": 24199.0,\n  \"avg\": 23862.10,\n  \"ema5\": 24021.51,\n  \"ema20\": 23761.42,\n  \"rsi\": 50.14,\n  \"support\": 24187.30,\n  \"bullish\": 23990.60,\n  \"warning\": \"Date changed from 23-Dec-2024 to 24-Dec-2024 — previous bar committed as history\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "200 — Early snapshot (before indicators seeded)",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "PUT",
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/update/{{ticker}}" },
                "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"date\":  \"01-Jan-2024\",\n  \"close\": 21500.0,\n  \"open\":  21480.0,\n  \"high\":  21550.0,\n  \"low\":   21450.0\n}"
                }
              },
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"ticker\": \"NIFTY\",\n  \"date\": \"01-Jan-2024\",\n  \"close\": 21500.0,\n  \"open\": 21480.0,\n  \"high\": 21550.0,\n  \"low\": 21450.0,\n  \"hl\": null,\n  \"avg\": null,\n  \"ema5\": null,\n  \"ema20\": null,\n  \"rsi\": null,\n  \"support\": null,\n  \"bullish\": null,\n  \"warning\": null\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Update ticker — force recompute",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/update/{{ticker}}?force=true",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "update", "{{ticker}}"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "force",
                  "value": "true",
                  "description": "Recompute support and bullish on every tick regardless of caching"
                }
              ]
            },
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"date\":  \"23-Dec-2024\",\n  \"close\": 23980.0,\n  \"open\":  24099.0,\n  \"high\":  24099.0,\n  \"low\":   23963.0\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Same as normal update but with ?force=true — support and bullish are recomputed on every call regardless of whether they were already computed for today. Useful for testing or comparing values across ticks."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Update second ticker",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/update/banknifty",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "update", "banknifty"]
            },
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"date\":  \"23-Dec-2024\",\n  \"close\": 51200.0,\n  \"open\":  51500.0,\n  \"high\":  51500.0,\n  \"low\":   51100.0\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Each ticker has independent state — state is keyed by ticker name in the URL path."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Streaming",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "SSE stream — subscribe to ticker",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/stream/{{ticker}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "stream", "{{ticker}}"]
            },
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "text/event-stream" }
            ],
            "description": "Opens a Server-Sent Events stream. Each PUT to /api/update/{ticker} pushes a TickerSnapshot event here.\n\nResponse is a long-lived connection — Postman will show events as they arrive.\n\nEvent format:\n  data: {\"ticker\":\"nifty\", \"close\":23963.0, ...}\n\nOpen this in a browser tab or use curl:\n  curl -N http://192.168.29.204:5001/api/stream/nifty"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Debug",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Debug — compute from manual inputs",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/debug/compute",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "debug", "compute"]
            },
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"ema5_pre\":  24043.086,\n  \"ema20_pre\": 24284.484,\n  \"prev_high\":  24065.8\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Compute support and bullish from manually supplied settled EMA state.\n\nFields:\n  ema5_pre   — EMA5 after all committed bars (Excel col AS of last settled row)\n  ema20_pre  — EMA20 after all committed bars (Excel col BN of last settled row)\n  prev_high  — Previous day's high — used as d+1 anchor for the support search\n\nAlgorithm:\n  Support : d+1=prev_high (fixed), d+2=d+3=trial, find trial where BP[d+3]=BP[d+2]\n  Bullish : d+1..d+4=trial, find trial where BP[d+4]=BP[d+3]\n            (self-referential: the price that generates itself as its own support)\n\nReturns CSV with support, bullish, and BP series at each result."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 — CSV trace",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/debug/compute" },
                "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"ema5_pre\":  24043.086,\n  \"ema20_pre\": 24284.484,\n  \"prev_high\":  24065.8\n}"
                }
              },
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "text/plain" }],
              "body": "field,value,description\nema5_pre,24043.086,Settled EMA5 (after all committed bars)\nema20_pre,24284.484,Settled EMA20 (after all committed bars)\nprev_high,24065.8,Previous day's high — d+1 anchor for support\n\nsupport,24215.80,brentq: d+1=prev_high d+2=d+3=trial BP[d+3]=BP[d+2]\n  BP_d1,-241.40,\n  BP_d2,-186.14,\n  BP_d3,-186.14,\n\nbullish,23958.47,brentq: d+1..d+4=trial BP[d+4]=BP[d+3]  (self-referential fixed point)\n  BP_d1,-202.66,\n  BP_d2,-202.66,\n  BP_d3,-202.66,\n  BP_d4,-202.66,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Debug — trace seeded ticker",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/debug/{{ticker}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "debug", "{{ticker}}"]
            },
            "description": "Show the futures computation trace for the current live state of a seeded ticker.\n\nUses the checkpoint (settled) EMA state and the last committed bar's high as prev_high.\nReturns the same CSV format as POST /api/debug/compute.\n\nRequires the ticker to be seeded (POST /api/seed/{ticker}) first.\nReturns 404 if ticker is not loaded, 400 if still in commit mode."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 — CSV trace",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/debug/{{ticker}}" }
              },
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "text/plain" }],
              "body": "field,value,description\nema5_pre,24043.086,Settled EMA5 (after all committed bars)\nema20_pre,24284.484,Settled EMA20 (after all committed bars)\nprev_high,24065.8,Previous day's high — d+1 anchor for support\n\nsupport,24215.80,brentq: d+1=prev_high d+2=d+3=trial BP[d+3]=BP[d+2]\n  ...\n\nbullish,23958.47,brentq: d+1..d+4=trial BP[d+4]=BP[d+3]  (self-referential fixed point)\n  ..."
            },
            {
              "name": "404 — Ticker not found",
              "status": "Not Found",
              "code": 404,
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/debug/{{ticker}}" }
              },
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"detail\": \"Ticker 'NIFTY' not found\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "400 — Commit mode (not seeded)",
              "status": "Bad Request",
              "code": 400,
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/debug/{{ticker}}" }
              },
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"detail\": \"Ticker is in commit mode — seed it first\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
